9:
The name's Lou. Lou Schwanz! One
adventurer registration form please!
12: Oh, hello there! Are you, er, a Gargan?
15:
Nope. But don't worry, I get that all
the time. I'm a proud canid!
18: Ah, sorry 'bout that. A canid, huh?
20: Say, you know this guy, Nimbus?
24:
Look, you can't assume that just
because I'm—
27:
Absolutely pathetic. The Guild's so
desparate for help, they'll take
ANYBODY these days!
31:
You got a problem with me or
somethin'?
34:
Scram, kid. You're makin' the booze
taste bad.
38: I don't think I like your 'tude, man!
39:
And if you ask me, I think you've had
enough booze!
42:
I'll tell you what I've had too much of.
Uppity little punks like you!
46:
All kinds o' freak shows have been
joinin' the guild lately...
47:
And now we've even got shaggy
furballs like you on the payroll!
55:
N-Nimbus! Y-you know me, I would
never—
59:
Nah, let's hear it! I'm sure you've got
plenty more to say about us
"furballs", right?
66:
I'd advise you to head home. Unless
you wish to end up like that table.
75: It looks like we owe you a new table.
78:
Not harm done—I'll just dock the
damages from your next payment.
82:
Phew, you really showed those
scaredy-cats a lesson, old-timer!
You were all like, RAWR! And then,
like, KA-PSHHH!
86:
Hold on... You're a cat? B-but how?
Uh, I mean... You wanna throw
down?!
90: Sheesh... You're comin' with me, kid.
95:
NOOO! Let me go, you crazy cat! I'll
have you know that I'm a proud
canid warrior!
101:
Whoa... What is this place?! Is
that—is that the world?! The clouds
are so FLOOFY! And the water... It's so
GLITTERY!
117:
Alk! We have a new canid... and he's
a pup!
126:
I'm only gonna say this one more
time, so listen up.
132:
You must've wandered far from
home to end up in Palpebra. But
with the World Flipper, you can
finally go home.
133:
I dunno if you missed the news, but
the cat and dog wars are
over—there ain't no reason for you
to fight.
134:
Got all that? So pack your things
and run home.
144: What... what do you mean why?
147:
I mean, I finally found my chance to
go on a real adventure! You're
telling me to go home after all this?
152:
No way, man! This is the perfect
opportunity for me to become a
REAL canid warrior!
157:
Well, we can't FORCE him to stay
here.
168:
I suppose that makes Nimbus his
carekeeper for the time being.
174: Huh? Why do I have to—
180:
Rad! You ready to rock and roll,
partner?
